        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Patch Set 2:\n> \n> it seems only \"$xyz\" is returned, instead of \"${xyz}\", the braces are missing \n> \n>                                 \"resource-name\": \"vdns_int_private_ip_0\",\n>                                 \"resource-value\": \"$vdns_int_private_ip_0\"\n\n\nHi Abdel, thanks for your update.\n\nI thought the default was $variable, not ${variable}. \n\nTo confirm, if I get $pnf-id and cannot resolve a value for it, I will attribute it to ${pnf-id}. Is that correct?\n\nIs this the only change that needs to be done?",
